What is Abstract?

Abstract is an Ethereum L2 designed for consumer facing applications across DeFi, SocialFi, NFTs, and more. Abstract is built on top of Ethereum using the ZK Stack. Abstract leverages advanced zero-knowledge cryptography to build a scalable blockchain that looks and feels like Ethereum, but with lower costs and higher throughput.

Abstract airdrop details

Abstract has officially launched its mainnet, inviting users to explore its ecosystem, deposit assets, and claim rewards.

In addition, Dinero has launched absETH, a new ETH staking solution on Abstract Chain that allows users to earn high ETH staking yields without leaving their preferred L2 networks.

Step-by-Step Guide:

Latest Update: Dinero Launches absETH Staking on Abstract Chain

How to Participate

  1. Visit the Dinero app
  2. Choose your source chain (Ethereum or Abstract)
  3. Stake your ETH to start earning yields

Key Features

  • ETH staking directly on Abstract Chain
  • High staking yields for ETH
  • Cross-chain compatibility powered by LayerZero
  • Accessible from multiple L2 networks

How to participate in Abstract mainnet 

  • Bridge to Abstract
    • Use your EVM wallet to bridge assets to Abstract via:
      • Jumper
      • Relay
  • Sign Up on Abstract Dashboard
    • Create an account using your wallet or email at Abstract Dashboard.
    • Deposit assets on the Abstract chain.
  • Connect Your Accounts
    • Link your X and Discord accounts to integrate fully with the Abstract ecosystem.
  • Participate in GameFi on Abstract
    • Join the Monsters.fun waitlist
    • Play games such as:
      • Gigaverse
      • Onchain Heroes
      • Penguin Life
      • Duper
      • Promotion Royale
  • Claim Badges and Rewards
    • Head to Abstract Rewards to earn and collect badges as you interact with the ecosystem.
    • Here are some of the badges discovered so far:
      • Multiply It: Go to Discover and click on the Multiplier app. Play at least one round of Multiplier.
      • Super Duper: Go to Discover, click on the Duper app. Connect your wallet to Duper and choose Tutorial Playground. Play at least one round and claim the badge by going to Rewards.
      • The Sock Master: Own a pair of the Abstract socks. There is a supply of only 500 and can be bought on the secondary market via DYLI.
      • Trailblazer: Go to Discover, scroll down and filter by Social. Click on Boost, then click on Go to Website. Enter your email address and provide the verification code that was sent to unlock the Trailblazer badge for registering early with Boost.
      • The Threadoor: Awarded to users who have made long-form content on X about Abstract.
      • Myriad Master: Go to Discover, scroll down and filter by Trading. Click on Myriad, set up your account and place a bet.
      • Giga Chad: awarded to Abstract Discord members that have the Giga role.
      • Abstract Elite: awarded to Abstract Discord members that have the Elite role.
      • Youre So Early: awarded to users who signed up to the Abstract waitlist before mainnet went live.
  • Trade Perps on Vertex
    • Trade perps on Vertex using USDC to earn Abstract XP
  • Explore the Ecosystem
    • Navigate to Discover to engage with various features and tools within Abstracts network

Abstract testnet participation

  1. Visit the Abstract testnet bridge page.
  2. Connect your wallet.
  3. Change the network to Ethereum Sepolia testnet.
  4. You will need some testnet ETH. You can get Sepolia ETH from here.
  5. Now bridge ETH from Sepolia to Abstract testnet.
  6. Also, bridge it back to Sepolia.
  7. Deposits from L1 to L2 take around ~15 minutes and withdrawals from L2 to L1 currently take up to 24 hours.
  8. For more information regarding the testnet, see this page.
  9. Also complete the Intract quests and claim Abstract NFT.
  10. They dont have their own token yet, but users who interact with the testnet bridge may get an airdrop if they launch their own token.

Receive early bird NFT

  1. Visit the Abstract website.
  2. Sign up with your email address to join the waitlist.
  3. You will receive an early bird NFT badge.
  4. You will receive a mail with additional details on how to claim the badge.
